snippet.title: Kamelot - Love You To Death (Cover by SIEG)
snippet.description:
Siegfried Song Facebook : http://www.facebook.com/SiegfriedSongOfficial
Symmetric Chaos Facebook : http://www.facebook.com/SymmetricChaos

Abandoned Project 07
Kamelot - Love You To Death (Covered in 2013)

After I had swore myself that I would never cover kamelot songs or even listen to them with certain reason then I have a huge crush on a girl and she wished to have my version of this. I have broken the rules of my life for her quite a bit and it was one of them. 

I didn't have any instrumental tracks at that time so I gave her just voice file. Today, I back to the time and remastered this one again for you.

If you like this song, please visit my facebook page.
Thank you.
